&lt;li data-leveltext=&quot;&quot; data-font=&quot;Symbol&quot;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Didn’t find a position that perfectly matches your interests or qualifications? No problem, we still want to hear from you!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;533&quot; data-end=&quot;826&quot;&gt;At &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.rtings.com/&quot;&gt;RTINGS.com&lt;/a&gt;, our mission is simple: help people find the best product for their needs. We’re building the world’s most trusted product review platform, and that takes a team of curious, driven people who care about helping others make better decisions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;828&quot; data-end=&quot;1084&quot;&gt;We’re always interested in meeting talented people who want to contribute to what we’re building. If you don’t see a role that fits your profile today, feel free to submit a spontaneous application and tell us how you think you could add value to the team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1086&quot; data-end=&quot;1194&quot;&gt;We review these applications when new opportunities open up across different teams and levels of experience.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Personality&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;You are a team player &amp;amp; driven&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;You are proactive&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;You are methodical and detail oriented&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;You like helping people. The whole purpose of our website is to help people find the best product for them&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Don&#39;t hesitate any longer, apply and come join our amazing team!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;RTINGS is an equal opportunity employer and is committed to promoting diversity and inclusion in the workplace.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;Join the World&#39;s Leading Product Review Company as a&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong data-stringify-type=&quot;bold&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Head of Digital Product&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;! Reporting to the Director of Product, you will own &lt;span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://RTINGS.com&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;RTINGS.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&#39;s digital product. Define its vision, strategy, roadmap, growth opportunities, and investment priorities, and be accountable for its long-term success, including identifying the people, capabilities, and resources needed to achieve that success.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;This is your opportunity to make a real impact in the industry. You&#39;ll dive deep into the latest technologies and your expertise and passion will be crucial in setting industry standards and driving innovation. Help shape the future of product reviews and become part of the trusted source consumers rely on to make informed purchasing decisions based on their needs!&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
